summary: Completed comprehensive testing of FlipFoundry eBay arbitrage platform. All core functionalities working correctly.
passed_tests: Homepage loads with FlipFoundry branding and content
Backend proxy (port 8001) correctly forwards to Next.js (port 3000)
GET /api/health returns 200 with proper health status
GET /api/search/status returns 200 with eBay configuration status
POST /api/search validation works correctly (400 for empty keywords, 400 for invalid JSON)
POST /api/search returns SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE when eBay API not configured (expected)
Demo mode search works - 'laptop' search returns 12 demo results in UI
All required security headers present (CSP, X-Frame-Options, HSTS, Referrer-Policy)
Navigation elements working (Features, How It Works, Get Started buttons)
